The architecture consists of a command-line interface that drives various subcommands, each utilizing the core `AmassEngine`. The engine orchestrates an event-driven system where plugins process discovery events and enrich asset data through external service integrations. All discovered assets are stored in a graph database following the Open Asset Model (OAM).

Sources: [README.md:10-10]()

## Core Components

### Command-Line Interface

Amass provides several subcommands for different aspects of asset discovery and analysis:

| Subcommand | Description |
|------------|-------------|
| `enum` | Performs DNS enumeration and asset discovery using the plugin ecosystem |
| `engine` | Runs the Amass engine service with GraphQL API for programmatic access |
| `assoc` | Analyzes associations between discovered assets and organizations |
| `subs` | Extracts and analyzes subdomain information from the graph database |
| `track` | Monitors changes in enumeration results over time |
| `viz` | Creates visualizations of discovered asset relationships |

The `enum` command is the primary interface for asset discovery, while `engine` provides a service-oriented approach. Analysis commands (`assoc`, `subs`, `track`, `viz`) operate on previously collected data stored in the graph database.

Sources: [README.md:10-10]()

### Event Processing Pipeline

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "Event Processing Architecture"
        EVENT_SOURCE["Asset Discovery Event"]
        DISPATCHER["EventDispatcher"]
        HANDLER_REGISTRY["HandlerRegistry"]
    end
    
    subgraph "DNS Discovery Plugins"
        DNS_TXT["DNS TXT Handler<br/>Priority: 1"]
        DNS_CNAME["DNS CNAME Handler<br/>Priority: 2"]
        DNS_IP["DNS IP Handler<br/>Priority: 3"]
        DNS_SUBS["DNS Subdomain Handler<br/>Priority: 4"]
        DNS_APEX["DNS Apex Handler<br/>Priority: 5"]
        DNS_REVERSE["DNS Reverse Handler<br/>Priority: 8"]
    end
    
    subgraph "API Enrichment Plugins"
        GLEIF_FUZZY["GLEIF Fuzzy Search"]
        GLEIF_RELATED["GLEIF Related Orgs"]
        AVIATO_SEARCH["Aviato Company Search"]
        AVIATO_ENRICH["Aviato Company Enrich"]
        AVIATO_EMPLOYEES["Aviato Employees"]
    end
    
    subgraph "Asset Database"
        FQDN_ASSETS["FQDN Assets"]
        IP_ASSETS["IP Address Assets"]
        ORG_ASSETS["Organization Assets"]
        PERSON_ASSETS["Person Assets"]
        CERT_ASSETS["Certificate Assets"]
    end
    
    EVENT_SOURCE --> DISPATCHER
    DISPATCHER --> HANDLER_REGISTRY
    
    HANDLER_REGISTRY --> DNS_TXT
    HANDLER_REGISTRY --> DNS_CNAME
    HANDLER_REGISTRY --> DNS_IP
    HANDLER_REGISTRY --> DNS_SUBS
    HANDLER_REGISTRY --> DNS_APEX
    HANDLER_REGISTRY --> DNS_REVERSE
    
    HANDLER_REGISTRY --> GLEIF_FUZZY
    HANDLER_REGISTRY --> GLEIF_RELATED
    HANDLER_REGISTRY --> AVIATO_SEARCH
    HANDLER_REGISTRY --> AVIATO_ENRICH
    HANDLER_REGISTRY --> AVIATO_EMPLOYEES
    
    DNS_TXT --> FQDN_ASSETS
