## Installation Methods

Amass supports multiple installation approaches to accommodate different deployment scenarios and user preferences.

### Installation from Go Modules

Amass can be installed directly from source using Go modules. This method provides the latest development version and is recommended for users who need cutting-edge features or want to contribute to development.

**Requirements:**
- Go 1.24.0 or later
- CGO disabled (`CGO_ENABLED=0`)

**Installation Command:**
```bash
go install github.com/owasp-amass/amass/v5/cmd/amass@latest
```

This installs the main `amass` binary along with all subcommand binaries to your `$GOPATH/bin` directory.

