### QPS Calculation

The maximum DNS queries per second is calculated using the formula:

```
MaxDNSQueries = (len(Resolvers) Ã— ResolversQPS) + (len(TrustedResolvers) Ã— TrustedQPS)
```

This ensures proper rate limiting across all configured resolver pools.

