The DNS System provides core DNS resolution capabilities and DNS-based asset discovery for OWASP Amass. It manages DNS resolver pools, performs various DNS record lookups, detects wildcard responses, and discovers network assets through systematic DNS enumeration. This system forms the foundation for domain and subdomain discovery, IP address resolution, and network infrastructure mapping.

