## Asset Storage and Relationship Creation

### DNS Record Property Storage

All DNS handlers follow a consistent pattern for storing DNS records as entity properties:

```go
// Standard DNS record property creation
_, err := e.Session.Cache().CreateEntityProperty(fqdn, &oamdns.DNSRecordProperty{
    PropertyName: "dns_record",
