### DNS Relationship Types

The system creates several types of DNS relationships in the graph database:

| Relation Type | Purpose | Source Handler |
|---------------|---------|----------------|
| `BasicDNSRelation` | A, AAAA, CNAME, PTR records | `dnsIP`, `dnsCNAME`, `dnsReverse` |
| `PrefDNSRelation` | MX records with preference | `dnsSubs` |
| `SRVDNSRelation` | SRV records with priority/weight | `dnsSubs` |
| `SimpleRelation` | Apex domain hierarchy | `dnsApex` |

