### TTL and Monitoring

Plugins implement time-to-live (TTL) controls to avoid redundant processing:

```go
// Check if asset was recently processed
since, err := support.TTLStartTime(e.Session.Config(), 
    string(oam.Organization), string(oam.Identifier), pluginName)

if support.AssetMonitoredWithinTTL(e.Session, e.Entity, src, since) {
    // Use cached results
    return cachedResults
} else {
    // Perform new query
    results := queryExternalAPI()
    support.MarkAssetMonitored(e.Session, e.Entity, src)
    return results
}
```

