## Summary

The network infrastructure in OWASP Amass provides a robust foundation for the various network-based reconnaissance techniques employed by the tool. It includes a carefully configured HTTP client, efficient web crawling capabilities, and specialized functions for extracting valuable information from TLS certificates. These components work together to enable Amass to discover a wide range of internet-facing assets associated with target organizations.

