## Data Storage and Relationships

The network mapping system creates a hierarchical relationship model in the asset database where IP addresses are contained within netblocks, and netblocks are announced by autonomous systems. This creates a navigable graph of network ownership and routing information.

| Asset Type | OAM Class | Key Properties | Relationships |
|------------|-----------|----------------|---------------|
| IP Address | `oamnet.IPAddress` | `Address`, `Type` | contained by Netblock |
| Netblock | `oamnet.Netblock` | `CIDR`, `Type` | contains IPs, announced by ASN |
| Autonomous System | `oamnet.AutonomousSystem` | `Number` | announces Netblocks |
| Registry Record | `oamreg.AutnumRecord` | `Handle`, `Name` | registration of ASN |

