## Service Asset Creation

When HTTP probes succeed, the system creates comprehensive service assets with detailed metadata:

| Service Property | Source | Description |
|-----------------|--------|-------------|
| `ID` | `ServiceWithIdentifier()` | Unique service identifier based on hash |
| `Output` | `resp.Body` | HTTP response body content |
| `OutputLen` | `resp.Length` | Response content length |
| `Attributes` | `resp.Header` | HTTP response headers |

Protocol determination follows this logic:
- Port 80 or 8080 â†’ `http` protocol
- All other ports â†’ `https` protocol  
- TLS certificates present â†’ `https` protocol

