## JARM Fingerprinting

The JARM fingerprinting plugin analyzes TLS implementations to create unique fingerprints for service identification:

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "JARM Plugin Flow"
        SERVICE_EVENT["Service Event"]
        CERT_CHECK["Certificate Presence Check"]
        JARM_QUERY["JARM Probing"]
        FINGERPRINT["Fingerprint Generation"]
    end
    
    subgraph "Probing Process"
        PORT_EDGES["Incoming Port Edges"]
        TARGET_FILTER["HTTPS Target Filter"]
