## Release Management

### Version Tagging Strategy

Releases are triggered by pushing version tags matching the pattern `v*.*.*` (semantic versioning). This triggers both the GoReleaser and Docker workflows simultaneously.

### Docker Image Tagging

The Docker workflow generates multiple tags for each release:
- `v{major}` - Major version tag
- `v{major}.{minor}` - Minor version tag  
- `v{major}.{minor}.{patch}` - Full version tag

