    EventProcessing["Event Processing<br/>handler.Callback()"]
    Stop["Plugin Stop<br/>plugin.Stop()"]
    
    PluginCreation --> Registration
    Registration --> Start
    Start --> HandlerReg
    HandlerReg --> EventProcessing
    EventProcessing --> EventProcessing
    EventProcessing --> Stop
```

